The list of platforms in violation of Freedom of Speech:
1. TWITTER - there are many alternatives to the micro-blogging platform, most of
   which are doing everything in their power to not be in violation of Freedom of
   Speech. Please consider these alternatives - Minds, Gab, Gettr
2. PATREON - there are a few alternatives to the creator funding platform, one
   of which is not only open, but also free - Liberapay

